caption:
This is SO good?! 🫣⁣
⁣
I KNOW shaving canned meat doesn’t sound sexy, but trust me, it works! The crispy, savory bite of this snack was unreal 👏🏽⁣
⁣
I mixed shredded meat with @omsom Saucy Noodles, shredded potatoes, eggs, and cheese, then air-fried it at 425°F for 20 minutes.⁣
⁣
The result was perfectly crispy bites, and dipping them in chili crisp mayo took them over the top ✨⁣
⁣
I loved how the shaved meat weaved into the noodles, making each bite extra delicious. This technique unlocks so many possibilities. Maybe make fried rice with shaved canned meat next? 👀⁣
⁣
Also… what do we call this?! Crispy noodle ball?! Help me name this snack 🤭⁣
⁣
